<textBlocks>
	<container id="formVBox">
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="25.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Step 2. Lay out goals for using ERB">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="The core team lays out 3 to 5 goals for going through the ERB process.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="It will help the core team select which activities to do in chapters 2-5, and whom to invite to participate in community workshops.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="What should our goals be? ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="It depends on whether your team has a specific charge (e.g., update county hazard mitigation plan, decide which projects to fund), disaster or climate problem (e.g., extreme heat, accidental radiological release), and societal concerns (e.g, youth incarceration, local economy).">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How to do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Hold a team meeting to work through the ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text="goals worksheet"
			linkType="externalDOC"
			link="Ch1_Goals_Worksheet.docx">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text=". It contains a pre-populated list of goals you can adapt, and guiding questions if you want to come up with your own goals. We've provided a ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text="goal setting scenario"
			linkType="internalStep"
			link="121">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text=" to help. You can also use the ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text="team storytelling results"
			linkType="externalDOC"
			link="Ch1_team_storytelling_results.docx">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text=". After the core team comes to consensus, fill in the goals section of the ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text="project plan"
			linkType="externalDOC"
			link="Ch1_Project_Plan_Template.docx">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text=". Pro tip: You can revise the goals at any time.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
	</container>
